{"tid":1944680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【鄭麗琼被捕】短片抹黑民主黨派錢　由警員拍攝？　警方僅七字回應","createTime":"2020-03-26T14:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T09:36:50.000Z","uid":73381,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eb436d60ed1ec7875b4044a0de12ffdd9f2e7bd0","tid":1944680,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:18:09.000Z","msg":"民主黨鄭麗琼今日凌晨被捕，多名黨友今早到警署聲援。網上流傳影片，拍攝到中西區區議員甘乃威疑向聲援人士「派錢」。民主黨事後解釋當時眾人只是夾錢保釋鄭麗琼，而非有人收錢示威，又質疑影片是從警署內拍攝，認為有警員「煽動謠言」。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》向警方發電郵查詢影片是否由警員拍攝及發布；有關做法有否違規；如何回應「煽動謠言」指控；以及會否跟進調查等。警方晚上以七字回應：「警方會了解事件。」<br />\n<br />\n今日有一段長約 16 秒的影片在親建制的群組流傳，顯示甘乃威向黨友許智峯等人「派錢」。不少親建制網民質疑是有人收錢聲援鄭麗琼。民主黨尹兆堅事後解釋，當時是因為警方突然將保釋金加至 10,000 元，一眾黨友正夾錢保釋鄭，甘乃威只是將多餘的金錢交還許智峯。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨亦在 FB 發文，強調眾人當時只是在夾錢，卻被「藍絲」抹黑成收錢示威。民主黨質疑影片是由警員於警署內拍攝：「咁又算唔算煽動謠言？警察犯法拉唔拉呀？」《立場》記者當時發現，當時的確有兩名男子站在警署內高位，其中一人高舉手機，疑是對警署門口拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%84%AD%E9%BA%97%E7%90%BC%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2-%E7%94%B1%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%83%85%E4%B8%83%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2584%25AD%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2590%25BC%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%258A%25B9%25E9%25BB%2591%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%258C%25A2-%25E7%2594%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%2594%259D-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2583%2585%25E4%25B8%2583%25E5%25AD%2597%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWRwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=332549de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2584%25AD%25E9%25BA%2597%25E7%2590%25BC%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%258A%25B9%25E9%25BB%2591%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%258C%25A2-%25E7%2594%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%2594%259D-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2583%2585%25E4%25B8%2583%25E5%25AD%2597%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589&h=ce93bd7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%84%AD%E9%BA%97%E7%90%BC%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2-%E7%94%B1%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%83%85%E4%B8%83%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89</a>"},{"pid":"3fe70d81603bbab70108ff6a91cd019ba98872e3","tid":1944680,"uid":254594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:19:16.000Z","msg":"咁快回力鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23862ae09e258f0cd1d554aaffd51dc254c85282","tid":1944680,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:19:17.000Z","msg":"算啦<br />\n警察就係法律"},{"pid":"b7ddc7ad220f29c1ecad1304120a8bf643f4b762","tid":1944680,"uid":133341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"黑警大撚哂"},{"pid":"28be7d44d4b524c194d5dea2af096babd560c3ad","tid":1944680,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5504f81a75571443696b96e0635806f40ec87d44","tid":1944680,"uid":175036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:25:17.000Z","msg":"泛民post正確資訊=煸動暴力<br />\n狗post誤導資訊=汪汪汪汪"},{"pid":"4859cc02815446757ed6a7bc11184ba719db6374","tid":1944680,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T14:26:18.000Z","msg":"以為係不評論個別事件"},{"pid":"5599c900fb5830252e38932ce660fecf666032c1","tid":1944680,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"睇死話帶左口罩認唔到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a33439dd8d675a9f2813126